{"tid":1941520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「點解叫漢他唔係種族歧視？」雲南返工包車爆漢他病毒疫情 已釀1死！","createTime":"2020-03-24T12:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T23:06:16.000Z","uid":58552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2b960300ac73e524982fcf48b151283f87fa26a6","tid":1941520,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:41:51.000Z","msg":"漢他病毒（Hantavirus），又譯漢坦病毒，是本雅病毒目的一種病毒，其引發的病症稱為漢他病/腎綜合徵出血熱/流行性出血熱，為一種經由老鼠傳染給人類的致命傳染病，被列為生物性危害第四級病毒，該病毒由李鎬汪於1978年在<span style=\"color: red;\">南韓漢灘江疫區</span>的黑線姬鼠肺組織中首度分離成功，因而得名。<br />\n<br />\n據官方通報，一輛由雲南開往山東的返工包車，昨天途經陝西被確診爆發漢他病毒出血熱疫情，該車33名乘客已有1人死亡，2人發燒，這3人對武漢肺炎病毒檢測呈陰性。<br />\n<br />\n點解無左膠無人幫韓國人出聲？污名化？<br />\nTwitter Hantavirus"},{"pid":"5fef734e90205b7fde28d4bd1a4c8120c0f59e5b","tid":1941520,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:44:49.000Z","msg":"啫又爆瘟疫？"},{"pid":"22e02a5ef20436ad045a22bac100a087ee7645fe","tid":1941520,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:46:04.000Z","msg":"係幾時發生？"},{"pid":"7c28c3018b28293c9a13a380266cb0915b2b0d3b","tid":1941520,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"22e02a5ef20436ad045a22bac100a087ee7645fe","tid":1941520,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:46:04.000Z","msg":"係幾時發生？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:56:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/acn/202003240249.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202003240249.aspx&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=d5117c92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/acn/202003240249.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"1219a98f8c445f135b4ff2ae09071f6f7d24c7ab","tid":1941520,"uid":227628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T23:06:16.000Z","msg":"鼠疫上年已經有"}]}